This is a big monthly release of Terminaux that brings some of the biggest new features and the most promising improvements to make your console applications more powerful!

### Changes

This release contains a variety of changes, including, but not limited to:

- `[+]` Added horizontal scrolling support
- `[+]` Added Prosery, Quote, and Separator writers
- `[+]` Added high-density and simple canvases
- `[+]` Added input locks
- `[*]` Improved handling of grapheme clusters
- `[*]` Improved handling of cell width estimation
- `[*]` Made several graphical writers accessible to CLI apps
- `[*]` General improvements and bug fixes

Review the commit history if you want to get a deep insight about the changes.

### Feedback?

If you have issues with this version, report to us by [making a new issue ticket](https://github.com/Aptivi/Terminaux/issues/new).

